ҳ—ЩRarchive/external_nushell_repo_backup/nushell.github.io/blog/2025-06-13-twin0303.mdЩ@227b19dbdde044a51c00dae59c2f5dbd99921ad38b41fdff66d9695ba57e12c0Щ"title: 'This Week in Nushell #303'‘ЩJBelatedly published Wednesday, July 9th for PRs the week ending 2025-06-13Ъ;



This week, @noahfraiture made the 
``http get``
 and 
``http post``
 commands smarter. Just using 
``http``
 will usually choose the right verb!
Also 
``clip copy``
 and 
``clip paste``
 are moving! You'll now find them in 
``std``
, rather than 
``std-rfc``
.
Thanks for all the great contributions this week!
’җҗЪҝTitle: title: 'This Week in Nushell #303'
Path: Belatedly published Wednesday, July 9th for PRs the week ending 2025-06-13
Content:




This week, @noahfraiture made the 
``http get``
 and 
``http post``
 commands smarter. Just using 
``http``
 will usually choose the right verb!
Also 
``clip copy``
 and 
``clip paste``
 are moving! You'll now find them in 
``std``
, rather than 
``std-rfc``
.
Thanks for all the great contributions this week!
